---
---

<section id="about" aria-label="About">
  <div class="s-header rv" style="margin-bottom:0;padding-bottom:0;border-bottom:none;">
    <p class="s-label">03 — About</p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-left">
      <h2 class="about-h2 rv">
        One consultant.<br><em>Full-stack</em> capability.
      </h2>
      <p class="about-p rv">
        I'm Chris — founder of now→next, operating from Voorburg, NL.
        I work with organisations that need senior expertise delivered
        without the overhead of a consultancy or the friction of a large team.
      </p>
      <p class="about-p rv">
        My background spans technology leadership, enterprise agile, and
        hands-on software delivery. I've led programs at scale and shipped
        products from scratch — and I know the difference between
        what sounds good in a workshop and what works in production.
      </p>
      <p class="about-p rv">
        My current edge is AI-powered development. I've been using
        AI coding tools since they existed. That means your project moves
        at a velocity most teams can't match — with senior engineering
        judgment guiding every decision.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-right rv rv-d1">
      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-n"><span class="hi">15</span>+</div>
          <div class="stat-lbl">Years in tech &amp; transformation</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-n"><span class="hi">3×</span></div>
          <div class="stat-lbl">Faster delivery with AI teams</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-n"><span class="hi">NL</span></div>
          <div class="stat-lbl">Based in Voorburg, Netherlands</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-n"><span class="hi">∅</span></div>
          <div class="stat-lbl">Days of methodology theater</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    padding: 8rem 3.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 5fr 4fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .about-h2 {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.2vw, 2.6rem);
    letter-spacing: -.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .about-h2 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); }

  .about-p {
    font-size: .95rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.78;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .stat {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 2.25rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: background .3s;
  }
  .stat:hover { background: var(--bg-3); }
  .stat::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--accent);
    transform: scaleY(0);
    transform-origin: bottom;
    transition: transform .4s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1);
  }
  .stat:hover::before { transform: scaleY(1); }

  .stat-n {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    letter-spacing: -.04em;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }
  .stat-n .hi { color: var(--accent); }

  .stat-lbl {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: .58rem;
    letter-spacing: .12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-mute);
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    section { padding: 5rem 1.75rem; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  }
</style>
